snippet.title: LATER ALLIGATOR Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer premiere for gooftastic, fully animated, fully alligated video game, Later Alligator! Coming September 5th from Emmy Award winning SmallBu with developers PillowFight! Wishlist it on steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/966320/Later_Alligator/
